title: The Sopranos - Full Series - Scene DVD Rips
description:
The Sopranos - Full Series - Scene DVD Rips

Eighty-six episodes in total!

Seasons 1 and 5 are ~700MB per episode. The rest are ~350MB per episode.

This torrent is similar to the one I posted on 06/11/2007: http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3710953/The_Sopranos_FULL_SERIES
Only Season 6b episodes are a different rip and a few more *.nfo files are included. Some files have been renamed to signify their internal staus.

Here&#039;s a full episode guide: http://www.tv.com/the-sopranos/show/314/episode_guide.html?season=0

For those interested, here is some info about the complete series being released as a set: http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Sopranos-The-Complete-Series/9919

From TFA:
The Sopranos - The Complete Series will arrive on November 11th, in a 33-disc package that will have 28 DVDs featuring all 86 episodes from the show&#039;s 6-season run, plus 2 DVDs full of bonus material (more on that in a moment), and 3 CDs full of music from the show&#039;s soundtrack. The box, which incorporates book-like material (56 pages of text and pictures) from and about the show, is said to weigh in at about 10 pounds!

Cost doesn&#039;t come cheap for this, as the price is $399.99 SRP (a typical 30%-off discount, which many retailers offer on new DVD releases, would make the street price on this around $279.99...but that&#039;s up to the individual retailers, of course, and your mileage may vary significantly!).
